name: rule_01
pattern: systemId == ""land"", moduleId == ""FT"", eventType == ""TO_SUSP"", reverse == ""N"", paymentDirection == ""IN"", debitCurrencyCode == ""INR"", creditCurrencyCode == ""INR""

name: rule_02
body:
when input: Input(systemId == "land", moduleId == "FT", eventType == "FROM_SUSP", reverse == "N", paymentDirection == "IN", debitCurrencyCode == "INR", creditCurrencyCode == "INR")
                                          then outputs.add(new Output("256050301", input.beneficiaryBankCode.equals("INSABR0000001") ? input.beneficiaryAccount : "3050000002015FRF001M", "", ""))

name: rule_03
body:
when input: Input(systemId == "land", moduleId == "FT", eventType == "TO_SUSP", reverse == "Y", paymentDirection == "IN", debitCurrencyCode == "INR", creditCurrencyCode == "INR")
                                          then outputs.add(new Output("256050301", "3060000002010INR001D", "", ""))
